          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How much does it cost to get started?",
            "question_heading_tag": "h3",
            "answer": "<p>Users begin with a one-time evaluation before any treatment decision is made. Ongoing monthly treatment only begins if approved.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_2": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What happens if I’m not eligible?",
            "question_heading_tag": "h3",
            "answer": "<p>Not every user will be a fit for treatment. If a provider determines treatment is not appropriate, Skinfluence will communicate that clearly.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_3": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How long until I may see visible improvement?",
            "question_heading_tag": "h3",
            "answer": "<p>Anti-aging care is designed for consistency over time. Skinfluence sets expectations around gradual, visible improvement rather than instant transformation.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_4": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is Skinfluence a subscription?",
            "question_heading_tag": "h3",
            "answer": "<p>If approved, treatment is designed as a recurring monthly model focused on continuity, maintenance, and ease.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
