          "settings": {
            "question": "What payment methods are accepted at your store?",
            "question_heading_tag": "h3",
            "answer": "<p>Our online store accepts a variety of payment methods to ensure a convenient shopping experience for our customers. We accept major credit cards, such as Visa, MasterCard, American Express, and Discover, as well as debit cards. Additionally, we offer support for digital payment platforms like PayPal, Apple Pay, and Google Pay. We are constantly working to expand our payment options to accommodate our customers' needs.</p>"
